videos.description: James Bolden pokes the ball free and takes it all the way to the rim for the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: West Virginia's Bolden  steals it, sinks layup

videos.description: Jevon Carter drills a 3-pointer after a diving offensive rebound from Daxter Miles Jr. in the first half.
videos.headline: West Virginia's hustle leads to Carter 3

videos.description: West Virginia head coach Bob Huggins doesn't have many good things to say about his team's first half performance.
videos.headline: Huggins not happy with first half

videos.description: Wesley Harris comes out of nowhere to slam home a put back dunk for the Mountaineers.
videos.headline: West Virginia's Harris throws down put back slam

videos.description: Daxter Miles Jr. gets the inbound pass from Jevon Carter and sinks it for the Mountaineers.
videos.headline: West Virginia's Miles drills deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Niem Stevenson gets the dish from Zach Smith and knocks down the deep ball for the Red Raiders.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Stevenson sinks corner 3 to tie

videos.description: Niem Stevenson launches up a desperation 3-pointer but can't connect for the Red Raiders in the loss against the Mountaineers.
videos.headline: Texas Tech misses shot for OT
